      <h1>Open source accounting software</h1>

      <p>
        <span itemprop="name">umsatz</span>is a <span itemprop="description">small, self-contained bookkeeping software</span> aimed mostly at freelancers and small businesses.
      </p>

      <p>The current version of umsatz has the following features:</p>

      <ul class="features">
        <li>support for double-entry bookkeeping</li>
        <li>support for multiple currencies</li>
        <li>support for multiple languages</li>
        <li>support for arbitrary accounts</li>
        <li>support for arbitrary fiscal periods</li>
        <li>support for quick search and filter</li>
        <li>support for pdf exports for your accountant</li>
        <li>automatic backups to multiple attached devices</li>
        <li>secured with two factor authentication (password + totp)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>The following features are planned for future version, while no deadline is given:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>full text search (even including text from your attachments)</li>
        <li>automatic bank account syncing (based on aqbanking)</li>
        <li>detailed account analytics</li>
      </ul>
